::Shadow Wing::

She checked the frequencies on her comm-link.  She noticed that she was 
being scanned.  By who or what she didn't know.  She suddenly got that 
nervous feeling in her stomach.  She held her gun close to her and walked 
out of the bridge.  She went down the hallway and looked out through the 
hole in the side of the ship. She could see forest surrounding ship through 
the hole.
"Oh boy."she whipsered. A wave of fear came over her. She knew that someone 
had to have survived the holocost that happened here.  She just hoped that 
who ever survived was Maximal and still could be found.
